# matches_clean.parquet is the historical-match dataset that scripts/03_simulate.py:702
# reads unconditionally in --live mode for form features. ~558KB. Without this
# whitelist the live workflow fails at the next sim invocation (same root cause
# as the joblib models being missing). Retrain via `python scripts/01_prepare_data.py`.
!data/processed/matches_clean.parquet
!models/metrics.json
# Trained Poisson goal models — committed because the workflow has no
